CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 13, 1965, pg. 24 reads: "Class B Kings - Here is the winning Coraopolis High School basketball team that grabbed the WPIAL Class B title against Braddock at the Pitt Field House, Monday night. The final score was 68-54.  Members of the starting five are shown in front row.  Left to right: Jim Strickland, John Spencer, Tom Santacroce, Clarence Sellers nad Rich Walker.  Coach Vic Blanchi is in the center of the picture, on the left. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Coraopolis High School basketball team, including in front row, left to right: Jim Strickland, John Spencer, Tom Santacroce, Clarence Sellers, and Rich Walker, Coach Vic Blanchi in center left, possibly in Pitt Field House
